	<Title>
		Cryotherapy of the esophagus
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Cryotherapy video shows use of extreme cold treatment for Barrett&apos;s esophagus and esophageal cancer.
	</Abstract>
	<Stream>
		<VideoFile>
